<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    /* CSS styles for the email */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #00A7E9;
      padding: 20px;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .message {
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #00A7E9;
      padding: 20px;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .ticket-details {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .ticket-details li {
      list-style-type: none;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      text-align: left;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Ticket Created Successfully!</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="message">
    <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>
    <p>Thank you for creating a support ticket. We have received your request and will address it as soon as possible.</p>
    <div class="ticket-details">
      <p>Ticket details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Ticket ID:</strong> <%= ticketId %></li>
        <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= ticketTitle %></li>
        <li><strong>Description:</strong> <%= ticketDescription %></li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= ticketStatus %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p>If you have any further questions or updates regarding this ticket, please feel free to reach out to us.</p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The <%= companyName %> Support Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© 2023 <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
